{"tid":453024,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[投票] 30個典型香港人性格","createTime":"2017-10-30T20:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T04:34:56.000Z","uid":153665,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1cd782294b0d4db8f6dd2db66c3539ef30c8b4","tid":453024,"uid":153665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T20:10:15.000Z","msg":"回港8年，發現身邊香港人或多或少都有以下特徵。你又同唔同意？或者身邊同事朋友多唔多呢啲特點？<br />\n投票可回覆號碼1-30<br />\n<br />\n1. 冷漠<br />\n2. 自私、自我中心<br />\n3. 極Defensive，自我保護意識過強<br />\n4. 唔鍾意笑（除非工作需要，但皮笑肉不笑）<br />\n5. 愛投訴，欠缺同理心<br />\n6. 挜挜拃拃、不好禮讓<br />\n7. 好易燥底，郁啲起晒鋼、同人嘈<br />\n8. 見高拜，見低踩<br />\n9. 憎人富貴嫌人貧<br />\n10. 極端資本主義、拜金<br />\n11. 只顧搵錢不理世事<br />\n12. 功利主義、唯利是圖<br />\n13. 滑頭、世界仔<br />\n14. 羊群心態，喜愛跟風<br />\n15. 井底之蛙但扮到咩都識<br />\n16. 喜歡批評別人、家婆心態，以主觀角度下定論<br />\n17. Stereotype，擺脫不了傳統思想<br />\n18. 對人對事抱有不開放心態<br />\n19. 鍾意標籤人，亦習慣被人標籤<br />\n20. 經常一竹篙打一船人<br />\n21. 愛認叻、成日扮嘢，要威、要巴閉<br />\n22. 自命不凡，唔識謙虛做人<br />\n23. 自我意識強，喜歡表現自己刷存在感<br />\n24. 極度在意他人眼光和睇法<br />\n25. 喜歡靠身外物提升自信心/身分地位<br />\n26. 愛追求名牌、追潮流<br />\n27. 愛揮霍、造成浪費<br />\n28. 極端「先敬羅衣後敬人」主義，會因為衣著睇唔起一個人<br />\n29. 會被一兩句吉利或不吉利的說話左右自己的決定 e.g. 唔著灰色鞋、戴綠色帽<br />\n30. 無知，不問世事"},{"pid":"6aeb70e59deb0e3f1869024c221a724c56b4834a","tid":453024,"uid":39738,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T20:12:07.000Z","msg":"31.投樓主老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d574e0069bc4597de9fdab4682a063369c2a6b80","tid":453024,"uid":154963,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T20:22:44.000Z","msg":"唔知點解明明你唔係搞緊gag但都好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42865286b86a514773fd596cbf44270aa94d594","tid":453024,"uid":65170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T20:46:23.000Z","msg":"可唔可以投全部"},{"pid":"f03e23bcc9e7c76bf658e274d9cdddd9705cef1e","tid":453024,"uid":146924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T21:21:46.000Z","msg":"講得好中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想俾更多香港人睇到佢地而家喺人心目中係變成咁"},{"pid":"df6c8085ca98709104d693cbc94fdd9547d43b70","tid":453024,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T22:41:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>31.投樓主老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n32. 睇TVB"},{"pid":"9cb7daf221751ed578751ed5564d06254d3229f7","tid":453024,"uid":29070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T22:48:30.000Z","msg":"一個字，閪。"},{"pid":"1b9f49b68425e5a926ed4707d44aab2f6de8f53b","tid":453024,"uid":52596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T23:11:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>挜挜拃拃</blockquote><br />\n有冇人知點讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175cc7631d6d47aa8419e2218edf90843bd05bb8","tid":453024,"uid":9003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T23:15:04.000Z","msg":"覺得好多時呢啲所謂特徵都係老個輩人多，<br />\n後生唔係冇，但覺得少好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7763acdf34b58b2b0cd4fc49f9a19687bb583f09","tid":453024,"uid":146924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得好多時呢啲所謂特徵都係老個輩人多，<br />\n後生唔係冇，但覺得少好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中至老年人士 50幾歲嗰啲唔少都係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1492e9741ab1a49eb06481248cef1ef5abfd7131","tid":453024,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:55:43.000Z","msg":"以上列表適用於所有人類"},{"pid":"61a20732672d9dc68b8099e7da8183eb54a4a83e","tid":453024,"uid":153665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T20:48:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>挜挜拃拃</blockquote><br />\n有冇人知點讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n Ah ah ja ja<br />\n廣東話嚟㗎😅"},{"pid":"f972f6ac5dd